### GET tous les ingrédients
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients?page=1&size=10

###

### GET ingrédient par id
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1

###

### GET stock d'un ingrédient
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stock?at=2024-01-06T12:00:00Z&unit=KG

###

### GET tous les plats
GET http://localhost:8080/dishes

###

### PUT commande
PUT http://localhost:8080/dishes/1/ingredients
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "ingredient": { "id": 1 },
    "quantity": 0.5,
    "unit": "KG"
  }
]

###

### Ingrédient inexistant
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/999

###

### Stock sans paramètres
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stock

###

### PUT sans body
PUT http://localhost:8080/dishes/1/ingredients

###


### GET stockMovements avec plage de dates
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stockMovements?from=2024-01-05T00:00:00Z&to=2024-01-06T23:59:59Z

###

### POST ajouter un mouvement
POST http://localhost:8080/ingredients/1/stockMovements
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "quantity": 2.5,
    "unit": "KG",
    "type": "IN"
  }
]

###

### Ingrédient inexistant
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/999/stockMovements?from=2024-01-01T00:00:00Z&to=2024-01-31T00:00:00Z